{"tid":1611214,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【文宣製作】元氣壽司&吉野家","createTime":"2019-10-02T01:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T14:52:11.000Z","uid":266045,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"febd6cccc249a106d8ac409ad0c2018ccb2209d8","tid":1611214,"uid":266045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:51:20.000Z","msg":"由於有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">日本人以為香港示威者</span></strong></span>破壞元氣壽司&amp;吉野家係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">反日行為</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nxNKGu6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnxNKGu6.jpg&h=5bc4fb64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我喺度諗係咪應該做啲文宣俾<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">身處喺日本嘅香港人喺</span></strong></span>日本嘅吉野家&amp;元氣壽司嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">鋪頭門口派俾日本人</span></strong></span>？<br />\n<br />\n有人喺大J嘅FB留言，話可唔可以邀請Yamauchi Yosuke幫手做文宣，因為佢係熟識香港現況嘅日本插畫家<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aREQB6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaREQB6d.jpg&h=af8f5a3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/YamasotoYosuke/status/1178838853102133248?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FYamasotoYosuke%2Fstatus%2F1178838853102133248%3Fs%3D19&d=9ZkxwAQN0Q6nkyzE8ymhdHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=3c48c668\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FYamasotoYosuke%2Fstatus%2F1178838853102133248%3Fs%3D19&h=d7d8673b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/YamasotoYosuke/status/1178838853102133248?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/asKEvqF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FasKEvqF.jpg&h=56c185bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n查看 Yamauchi Yosuke (@YamasotoYosuke)：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/YamasotoYosuke?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FYamasotoYosuke%3Fs%3D09&d=9ZkxwAQN0Q6nkyzE8ymhdHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=4252429a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/YamasotoYosuke?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n當然如果有手足想自己製作亦都得！"},{"pid":"216fa1dd99302edf82f2b70e1a719fe664c5bca5","tid":1611214,"uid":266045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:57:01.000Z","msg":"p牌無人理💀"},{"pid":"1db5e78c98cc2aa1c6d7cad205257d8a4140c6fb","tid":1611214,"uid":266045,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:57:13.000Z","msg":"推唔郁💀"},{"pid":"e82daa32ab79669ccf8f5491dc9446c395b9d52f","tid":1611214,"uid":266045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:57:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205f7eb17f5a2a112db1520d34e912bf56f3ba7a","tid":1611214,"uid":250557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:57:42.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"4942119c5bc5115bbe08157e6b7ba253781c4f82","tid":1611214,"uid":266045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:57:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d7f5632f48074f4b10c08a29be8bb97451a9177","tid":1611214,"uid":266045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"205f7eb17f5a2a112db1520d34e912bf56f3ba7a","tid":1611214,"uid":250557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:57:42.000Z","msg":"推呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:58:42.000Z","msg":"多謝幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\